com.mapzen.places.api.ui

Class PlaceAutocomplete

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mapzen.places.api.ui.PlaceAutocomplete

  • public class PlaceAutocomplete
extends java.lang.Object
    Main entry point for the autocomplete API. A search widget is presented and users can select autocomplete results. Unlike the PlacePicker API, a map is not shown.
